In order to use this library project, please follow these instructions:

- Create an android project which references this project as library, means your new project contains an entry in the default properties like:
android.library.reference.1=../android-lib
where it points to this project

- Copy the file build-custom.xml to the root of your project
- run "ant -f build-custom.xml -Dnew.package.name=com.eventorama.mobi.whatever" 
Where you pass the package name of your project as parameter

Then build normally like
ant clean install

Have fun!
